    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Record a vote on behalf of a voter via the trusted recorder service.\\n\\nRequires the \"recorder\" role.\\n\\nThis is the primary API integration path. Eligibility and tier are verified\\noff-chain; the supplied `tier` is the authoritative vote weight source.\\n\\n# Arguments\\n* `caller`    - Recorder address (must have recorder role)\\n* `voter`     - Address of the voter\\n* `round_id`  - Active governance round ID\\n* `option_id` - Option to vote for\\n* `vote_type` - Up or Down\\n* `tier`      - Voter's NFT tier (verified off-chain by the API)\\n\\n# Returns\\nThe vote weight applied",
      "name": "record_vote",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "caller",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "voter",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "round_id",
          "type_": "u32"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "option_id",
          "type_": "u32"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "vote_type",
          "type_": {
            "udt": {
              "name": "VoteType"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "tier",
          "type_": {
            "udt": {
              "name": "NftTier"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        "u32"
      ]
    }
  },
